Isabella Patricola https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Isabella_Patricola 0 Isabella Patricola (1886 – May 23, 1965), known professionally by her stage name "Miss Patricola," was an American vaudeville performer popular in the 1920s. She was the sister of entertainer Tom Patricola.
